data.title: Catherine Hickland Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Catherine Hickland on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Catherine Hickland including Witchery and Robowar.
data.text:
Sex Club

When the new owner of an infamous playboy's (Peter Bogdanovich) address book is found murdered, detectives suspect a U.S. senatorial candidate, whose infidelity is documented in the book.

Let It Be Me

Michael is called upon by an old girlfriend, Stevie March, to uncover who murdered Greg Noble, the co-lead singer in the rock group "Class Action." In order to investigate the murder, Michael must join the band as the new lead singer. Soon, those who murdered Greg become suspicious of Michael and Stevie and they plot to kill them both.
